          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Distracted Driving Education Act of 2017&nbsp;</strong></p> <p>This bill directs the Department of Transportation (DOT) to establish a distracted driving education grant program under which DOT may make a competitive grant to a nonprofit organization to provide education to the public regarding the risks of distracted driving. </p>]]></text>
